data.description: This home, in a section of Vanguard Village that IS NOT 55+ has an open, airy floor plan with lovely touches. Enjoy the updated kitchen with granite countertops that offer plenty of counter space and room to create your culinary masterpiece! Tiled throughout and freshly painted, with a bright interior, plenty of windows to allow natural light and fresh air during the cooler months. While you're enjoying the fresh air, check out the new screened-in porch and enjoy the mild South FLA weather.Explore the community, and enjoy all its amenities, that include a community pool, playground and pond an easy walk from home.If buyer qualifies for a VA mortgage, the Seller's mortgage is assumable; they are willing to work with a buyer to explore the possibilities.
